OL,3,CMan who pretended to be police to
OL,4,Csteal #107,000 worth cars jailed
OL,6,FAn "incredibly calculated" man who
OL,7,Fpretended to be a police officer to
OL,8,Fgain the trust of people who were
OL,9,Fselling their cars - which he then
OL,10,Fdrove away with - has been jailed.
OL,12,FMason Crozier, 25, of Old Bank Avenue,
OL,13,FManchester, defrauded seven people
OL,14,Facross the North West of England and
OL,15,Fthe Midlands by impersonating an
OL,16,Fofficer and convincing them he had
OL,17,Ftransferred the money to buy their
OL,18,Fcars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
