OL,3,CMan who pretended to be police to
OL,4,Csteal #107,000 worth cars jailed
OL,6,FCrozier arranged to view a car for
OL,7,Fsale in Leicestershire on 11 May 2025,
OL,8,Fthat was previously owned by Greater
OL,9,FManchester Police, stating he wanted
OL,10,Fto buy it as he had previously driven
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,FHe then told the victim the purchase
OL,14,Fwas pending via his bank, gaining
OL,15,Ftheir trust by showing them payments
OL,16,Ffrom an apparent policing organisation
OL,17,Fon his online banking, but he then
OL,18,Fleft with the vehicle and the payment
OL,19,Fwas not received.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
