OL,3,CMan who pretended to be police to
OL,4,Csteal #107,000 worth cars jailed
OL,6,FCrozier took another car in Blackburn,
OL,7,FLancashire, for a test drive on 10
OL,8,FJune, telling the victim he would pay
OL,9,Fvia bank transfer but saying he had to
OL,10,Fleave as he was "on shift".
OL,12,FOn 17 June, Crozier used a similar
OL,13,Fmethod when viewing an Audi in Buxton,
OL,14,FDerbyshire, showing the victim images
OL,15,Fof his police badge and police warrant
OL,16,Fcard, before he took the vehicle
OL,17,F"while waiting for the payment to go
OL,18,Fthrough".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
