OL,11,FCrozier used similar tactics to steal
OL,12,Fa further four cars around Cheshire,
OL,13,FChester and Blackburn between 21 June
OL,14,Fand 24 August, showing a fake police
OL,15,FID and warrant card.
OL,17,FHe was arrested in Manchester on 1
OL,18,FSeptember 2025, having been identified
OL,19,Fas a suspect due to previous
OL,20,Fconvictions for similar offences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
