OL,3,CMan who pretended to be police to
OL,4,Csteal #107,000 worth cars jailed
OL,6,FCrozier was sentenced to three years
OL,7,Fand four months in prison at Chester
OL,8,FCrown Court on Monday, 5 January.
OL,10,FHe had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fseven counts of fraud by false
OL,12,Frepresentation, seven counts of
OL,13,Fimpersonating a police officer, and
OL,14,Fone count of possession of an article
OL,15,Ffor use in fraud.
OL,17,FThe total value of the stolen vehicles
OL,18,Fwas #107,585.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
